TCW's Sri-Kumar Likes Utilities, Consumer Staples: Audio

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-26T18:02:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/tcw-s-sri-kumar-likes-utilities-consumer-staples-audio.html
Komal Sri-Kumar, chief global 
strategist at TCW Group Inc., says he is telling investors to 
look at consumer staples, utilities and generally "defensive" 
stocks. Sri-Kumar talks with Ken Prewitt and Tom Keene on 
Bloomberg Radio's "Bloomberg Surveillance."   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 16:18
 